    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve"><head>Text</head><div n="1" type="textpart"><ab><lb n="1"/>
                <expan><abbr>I</abbr><ex>nvicto</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>O</abbr><ex>ptimo</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>M</abbr><ex>aximo</ex></expan> <lb n="2"/>Patrio </ab></div><div n="2" type="textpart"><ab><lb n="1"/> Iunoni <expan><abbr>Reg</abbr><ex>inae</ex></expan> </ab></div><div n="3" type="textpart"><ab><lb n="1"/> pro salute sua <lb n="2"/><expan><abbr>suorumq</abbr><ex>ue</ex></expan> omnium <lb n="3"/><expan><abbr>Aur</abbr><ex>elius</ex></expan> Marcellus qu<lb break="no" n="4"/>od miles vota<lb break="no" n="5"/>vit <expan><abbr>vet</abbr><ex>eranus</ex></expan> solvit <lb n="6"/><expan><abbr>IImmpp</abbr><ex>eratoribus</ex></expan> <lb n="7"/><expan><abbr>d<am>d</am></abbr><ex>ominis</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>n<am>n</am></abbr><ex>ostris</ex></expan> Maximiano <lb n="8"/><expan><abbr>Aug</abbr><ex>usto</ex></expan> V et Maximia<lb break="no" n="9"/>no <expan><abbr>nob</abbr><ex>ilissimo</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>Caes</abbr><ex>are</ex></expan> II co<expan><ex>n</ex><abbr>s</abbr><ex>ulibus</ex></expan> </ab></div><div n="4" type="textpart"><ab><lb n="1"/> <expan><abbr>v</abbr><ex>otum</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>l</abbr><ex>ibens</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>s</abbr><ex>olvit</ex></expan>
            </ab></div></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Z. 1-3 befinden sich auf der corona (davon Z. 3 auf dem Profil), Z. 13 auf der crepido. Die rechte obere Ecke des Altars mit dem vollständigen Text der Zeilen 1-4 war früher noch vorhanden. (B): Finály, AE 1926: Z. 1: I(nvicto) M(ithrae) oder I(ovi) [O(ptimo)] M(aximo); Z. 7/8: vo/vit. Am linken Rand der Corona ein eingeritzter Palmzweig.</p>
            </div>
